These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, ivory, fuchsia, amber, blood-red
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, ship, snowmobile, van
 1. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 2. the person who likes ebony is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
 8. the person who likes blood-red is not the person driving the ship##6
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
10. the person driving the boat is not the person who likes amber##6
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person driving the ship##7
15. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Color        | ivory | fuchsia | blood-red | amber     | ebony    |
| Transport   | ship | van       | boat   | snowmobile | motorbike |

