.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, lemonade, cola, sprite
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, british, malaysian, thai
 1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the thai is not to the left of the argentine##8
 3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 6. the brazilian is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 7. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite    | iced-tea | water  | lemonade |
| Nationality   | argentine  | malaysian | thai      | brazilian | british |

