.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, water, sprite, mirinda
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, house, indie
1. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the person drinking juice is between the fan of house and the person drinking sprite##2
4. the person drinking juice is the fan of folk##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage           | sprite | juice | mirinda | soy-milk | water  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | folk        | house          | indie     | classical |

