.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, german, indonesian, polish
House: farmhouse, cottage, wooden, tower, craftsman
 1. the argentine is somewhere between the brazilian and the farmhouse house##7
 2. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
 3. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 5. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 6. the cottage house is not the german##6
 7. the brazilian is on the right of the argentine##1
 8. the polish is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 9. the cottage house is somewhere between the german and the argentine##7
10. the cottage house is not to the right of the brazilian##8
11. the indonesian is the indonesian##1
12. the cottage house is not the indonesian##6
13. the tower house is on the right of the indonesian##1
14. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the german##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Nationality   | german | polish | indonesian | argentine | brazilian |
| House           | farmhouse    | cottage | craftsman    | tower      | wooden      |

