.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, mirinda, water
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, yellow, grey, amber, pink
 1. the person who likes amber is not to the left of the person who likes pink##8
 2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
 3. the person drinking water is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes amber##2
 4. the person who likes pink is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 8. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking water##2
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
10. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4   |    5    |
| Beverage      | fanta   | cola  | milk    | water | mirinda |
| Color   | aquamarine | pink | amber | yellow | grey   |

