.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-6::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, aquamarine, ivory, amber, yellow
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, scooter, train, tram, trike
 1. the person who likes amber is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person who likes amber##8
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person who likes chestnut##7
 6. the person who likes yellow is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes amber##7
 7. the person driving the trike is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes ivory and the person who likes yellow##2
 9. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the trike##8
10. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Color    | ivory | amber | yellow     | chestnut | aquamarine |
| Transport   | train    | trike    | scooter | bus         | tram   |

