.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-7::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, reading, gardening, sudoku, dancing
5 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, fish, frog, mouse
 1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
 2. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the frog##7
 5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 6. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
 7. the owner of the frog is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
10. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |   3    |   4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | gardening | reading | sudoku | dancing | camping |
| Pet           | mouse     | cat       | ferret | frog   | fish      |

