The people use 5 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, ship, subway
 1. the person driving the helicopter is not the blend-smoker##6
 2. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
 3. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
 5. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 6. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the chaman-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the car##7
10. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
11. the chaman-smoker is not the person driving the car##6
12. the blend-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |  4   |    5    |
| Cigar   | siglo    | chaman      | blend | pall-mall | bolivar |
| Transport     | motorbike | helicopter | ship    | car  | subway  |

