.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-15::.
5 different games are played: domino, whist, billiard, bridge, poker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, funk, pop, salsa
 1. the fan of folk is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
 2. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing domino is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 4. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 5. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 6. the person playing whist is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
 7. the fan of funk is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
 8. the fan of folk is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 9. the fan of salsa is the person playing whist##1
10. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
11. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
12. the person playing billiard is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of pop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |  3  |  4   |      5      |
| Game      | bridge | whist | poker | billiard | domino |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | salsa         | pop | folk | dubstep     |

