 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 6. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person watching zombie movies##8
 8. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person driving the taxi##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |      3      |     4     |       5       |
